column191: participantComments:"I wasn't sure if the object of the game was to score the most points or not.  Because if it is a co-op game the people should have gone to the center each time together since that would yield the most berries.  If the object was to get the most berries then they should have gone to the small bushes each time because you are guaranteed at least a tie since best case scenario you would get 5 berries each time and your opponent would only get 1 if they went to the center tree.  "
